ABI: sysfs-class-tpm: use wildcards for pcr-* nodes

Change how this expression is defined:

	/sys/class/tpm/tpmX/pcr-H/N

in order to allow get_abi.pl to convert it into this regex:

	/sys/class/tpm/tpmX/pcr-.*/.*

